    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken meticulous care of it\u2014not a single scratch or smudge in sight. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel that's so hard to find. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
