    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric engineering. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, it features individual throttle bodies and an overhauled VANOS system for precise variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with documented rod bearing replacement and a fully reinforced rear subframe to mitigate chassis fatigue. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Every bushing is compliant, the cooling system is refreshed, and the undercarriage is free of fluid seepage or oxidation. This is a concours-ready specimen optimized for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
