    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, featuring a factory-original finish that remains deep, glossy, and entirely free of imperfections, swirls, or stone chips. The interior is a time capsule, boasting supple, unworn leather, the original new-car scent, and high-definition displays that function with out-of-the-box precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, supported by a documented history of preventative maintenance and exceptionally low mileage. Every detail, from the pristine undercarriage to the flawless alloy wheels, reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-standard example that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
      "price": 48500.0,
